    description: 'From South Charlotte to Matthews, Ballantyne to Plaza Midwood—we\'ve worked on homes just like yours.',
    icon: 'star'
  },
  {
    title: 'Fully Insured',
    description: 'Full liability coverage on every project. Your home is protected, and so are we.',
    icon: 'shield'
  },
  {
    title: '5+ Years in Charlotte',
    description: 'We\'ve been serving Charlotte homeowners since 2019. Our reputation is built one project at a time.',
